==English==

=== Noun ===
'''mock'''
# an [[imitation]], usually connotation is one of lesser quality

==== Translations ====
*Dutch: [[imitatie]]
*German: [[Nachahmung]] ''f''
*Portuguese: [[simulado]]

=== Verb ===
'''to mock''' ([[mocks]], [[mocked]], [[mocking]])

# to [[mimic]], to [[simulate]]
# to make fun of by mimicking, to [[taunt]]

==== Translations ====
*Dutch: [[imiteren]] (1), [[naäpen]] (1), [[nadoen]] (1)
*French: [[imiter]] (1)
*German: [[nachahmen]] (1), [[trotzen]] (2)
*Hebrew: [[סנט|סָנַט]]
*Portuguese: [[simular]] (1)
*Russian: [[передразнивать]]

